Title: MDA.Net
Description:
MDA.Net is the .Net/Silverlight port of mda-vst instruments and effects.
Currently it includes just the MDA piano and an overdrive with basic interfaces to build on. Just PM me if you have some time to help - we are in no rush, aim to migrate everything one-by-one.
